PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781002969
OL,3,CLondon robotaxis could be available to
OL,4,Chire 'within months'
OL,6,F"Data is fed into our computer and
OL,7,Fthen the model recognises the images
OL,8,Fand understands what decisions it
OL,9,Fneeds to make and so it's ultimately
OL,10,Fthe software and the model which are
OL,11,Fmaking these decisions."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Waymo, the autonomous
OL,14,Fdriving company owned by Google parent
OL,15,Fcompany Alphabet, is also preparing to
OL,16,Flaunch a London service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
