PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781002969
OL,3,CLondon robotaxis could be available to
OL,4,Chire 'within months'
OL,6,FThe company says data from its
OL,7,Foperations in the United States shows
OL,8,Frobotaxis are 13 times less likely to
OL,9,Fbe involved in injury-causing crashes
OL,10,Fthan human-driven taxis.
OL,12,FNot everyone is convinced.
OL,14,FLondon cab driver Dale Forwood said:
OL,15,F"I see them every day, it's really
OL,16,Fworrying because they're blocking up
OL,17,Fthe roads and making big mistakes.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781002969
OL,3,CLondon robotaxis could be available to
OL,4,Chire 'within months'
OL,6,F"Our roads are not catered for it.
OL,7,FWe've got tiny little roads, San
OL,8,FFrancisco has got big straight roads
OL,9,Fso that's why it's working there. It's
OL,10,Fnot going to work here."
OL,12,FBoth Waymo and Wayve still require
OL,13,Fregulatory approval before fully
OL,14,Flaunching services in London.
OL,16,FUber says it hopes that approval could
OL,17,Fcome within months and has opened pre-
OL,18,Fregistration for customers interested
OL,19,Fin using robotaxis.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
