FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781002969
OL,3,CLondon robotaxis could be available to
OL,4,Chire 'within months'
OL,6,FAnnie Dunjak, head of Uber's
OL,7,FAutonomous Vehicles division, said
OL,8,Ffares would be the same as those
OL,9,Fcharged for journeys with human
OL,10,Fdrivers.
OL,12,F"As we've launched in multiple cities
OL,13,Fwe actually see that riders love it
OL,14,Fthere is magic as you get into the
OL,15,Fback of the car and it all of a sudden
OL,16,Fjust rides away but what's really
OL,17,Finteresting is you don't actually
OL,18,Fnotice it after a while"
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
