FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781002969
OL,3,CLondon robotaxis could be available to
OL,4,Chire 'within months'
OL,6,FThe London Assembly Transport
OL,7,FCommittee is due to discuss the
OL,8,Flicensing of autonomous vehicles on
OL,9,FTuesday.
OL,11,FEven if approval is granted, human
OL,12,Fsafety operators will still be
OL,13,Frequired to sit in the driver's seat
OL,14,Fduring the initial rollout.
OL,16,FThat means any impact on driving jobs
OL,17,Fis unlikely to be felt immediately.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
